import { Tabs, Tab, Toolbar, Typography,Button } from '@mui/material';
import AppBar from '@mui/material/AppBar';

export const Navbar = () => {



    return (
        <>
            <AppBar elevation={0}>
                <Toolbar disableGutters sx={{ p: 3, ml: 5 }} >
                    <Tabs sx={{ display: 'flex' }} textColor="primary">
                        <Tab >
                            <Typography>
                                Logo
                            </Typography>
                        </Tab>
                        <Tab label='HOME' />
                        <Tab label='What is GPT?' />
                        <Tab label='OPEN AI' />
                        <Tab label='CASE STUDIES' />
                        <Tab label='Library' />

                    </Tabs>
                    <Tab label="SIGN IN" />
                    <Tab>
                        <Button
                        variant="contained"
                        color='secondary'
                        >
                            Sign UP

                        </Button>
                    </Tab>

                </Toolbar>

            </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}
